    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use any piece of polished metal at least the size of a dagger as a scrying device, as if using the spell @Compendium[pf1.spells.g66w32kdup1f43bp]{Scrying}.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, this functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.glt6uk3n6g6l2p6l]{Scrying, Greater}.</p>\n<p>You can scry for a number of rounds per day equal to your oracle level; these rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
